What IS TuBallRx ?
The TuballRx is a resistance band with a ball on one side and a strap handle on
the other. Using the ball one can pull more resistance, have a good grip and
strengthen fingers and wrist at the same time. The other side is the strap
handle which can be held in the hand or put around the foot to allow for
stability during the dynamic exercise execution. The length of the tube is
perfect for a full body workout for upper and for lower body. The different
resistances of the bands from yellow (light), to green, red and blue (heavy)
allow for enough resistance for everyone.
The TuballRx was patented by the United States Patent Office in 2019
